per million = total reads/1000000
RPM = counts/permillion
RPKM = RPM/length(gene)[kb]
note: RPKM是对于单端测序来讲的，一条reads对应一个片段，FPKM是对于双端测序来讲，两条reads对应一个片段。所以，FPKM的计算跟RPKM是一致的，只不过在计算total reads时只需要计算一端的reads数。

RPK = counts/length(gene)[kb]
per million = sum(RPK)[a sample]/1000000
TPM = RPK/per million
method: R package "scater" "SingleCellExperiment"

来源：RPM, RPKM, FPKM, TPM...
http://www.rna-seqblog.com/rpkm-fpkm-and-tpm-clearly-explained/
